{"tid":917334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馮檢基：比以往鎅得「更深更痛」","createTime":"2018-11-26T10:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T10:51:18.000Z","uid":86509,"like":17,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8102f790b27d61522a3c2d269926eab7fbd0771c","tid":917334,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:40:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20151122/s00001/1448160821568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20151122%2Fs00001%2F1448160821568&d=Whuuq17inbS6e5jWNpwJAtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a473e367\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20151122%2Fs00001%2F1448160821568&h=5cb8e44d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20151122/s00001/1448160821568</a><br />\n<br />\n民協唯一立法會議員馮檢基出選深水埗麗閣邨選區，馮今早站在投票站外，與前來投票站前的選民揮手，但因投票站外屬禁止拉票區，他沒有攜帶任何宣傳物品。有身穿校服的中學生投票後與他合照。馮檢基指，11時前是老人家投票高峰期，自己要把握時機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馮檢基承認，今次選舉是他自2003年當選當區區議員起選情最嚴峻的一次。他說，前來「鎅票」的前民協成員黃仲棋，票源完全與他重疊，比以往鎅得「更深更痛」。<br />\n<br />\n他指，無論工聯會對手陳穎欣或黃仲棋今次都有心思部署，勢要「搣走馮檢基」，競爭比以往強很多。他暫不評估勝選，但承認支持度或有變化，可能長者會因對方物質資源影響而轉態支持對手。<br />\n<br />\n馮檢基又強調希望用政績取勝，花了5年時間令深水埗烏鴉數量驟減，又解決區內蚊患鼠患問題。"},{"pid":"36044fd7edaf557124b963fd93a44177489e6018","tid":917334,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:43:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3bc2874456b97f68f9657315da2248a860c98e","tid":917334,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bf84ddb88eccdebae9402dc8100515a5cd1e36","tid":917334,"uid":20058,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"連登仔扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" 